<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 16:10:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡总理“强烈谴责”士兵被拘留后闯入斯德泰曼监狱的行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/pm-netanyahu-strongly-condemns-break-in-into-sde-teiman-prison-over-soldiers-detention/00000190-fecd-d22a-abfe-ffed159c0000</link><description>九名涉嫌折磨一名巴勒斯坦被拘留者的士兵被拘留在斯德泰曼拘留中心，以及随后在该地点发生的冲突，引起了以色列政界的强烈反应。艾萨克·赫尔佐格总统说：“我们不要忘记，我们的敌人一次又一次地试图追捕我们，在国际法律舞台上也是如此。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 16:02:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/pm-netanyahu-strongly-condemns-break-in-into-sde-teiman-prison-over-soldiers-detention/00000190-fecd-d22a-abfe-ffed159c0000</guid></item><item><title>杀害约旦河西岸以色列狱警的巴勒斯坦嫌疑人供认不讳</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-suspect-in-killing-of-israeli-prison-guard-in-west-bank-confesses/00000190-feb7-da9d-abff-ffff5a5e0000</link><description>军事法庭延长了对西岸银行嫌疑人易卜拉欣·曼苏尔的拘留令，据称他于 7 月初在吉文·哈达沙定居点杀害了尤海·阿夫尼，但杀人动机仍不清楚</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 15:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-suspect-in-killing-of-israeli-prison-guard-in-west-bank-confesses/00000190-feb7-da9d-abff-ffff5a5e0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔因不当行为调查而撤回以色列警察局长人选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-pick-for-israel-police-chief-withdraws-amid-investigations-of-misconduct/00000190-fecd-da63-a9d0-ffed93d20000</link><description>现任代理警察局长阿夫沙洛姆·佩莱德 (Avshalom Peled) 被曝因违反信任而受到多项调查，这导致他的任命被推迟。佩莱德退出后，本-格维尔提出了新候选人</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 15:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-pick-for-israel-police-chief-withdraws-amid-investigations-of-misconduct/00000190-fecd-da63-a9d0-ffed93d20000</guid></item><item><title>对 Majdal Shams 悲剧的反应表明阿拉伯人对以色列的德鲁兹人感到困惑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/reactions-to-majdal-shams-tragedy-show-arab-confusion-about-the-druze-in-israel/00000190-fdc8-d807-a1b2-ffebb6ea0000</link><description>社交媒体上的一些人庆祝戈兰高地发生的致命袭击，这场袭击造成 12 名儿童死亡，以此作为对以色列轰炸加沙的报复。其他人质疑在了解以色列的德鲁兹人复杂的历史之前是否应该同情他们</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 14:35:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/reactions-to-majdal-shams-tragedy-show-arab-confusion-about-the-druze-in-israel/00000190-fdc8-d807-a1b2-ffebb6ea0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么巴黎奥运会开幕式激怒了欧洲极右翼分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-enrages-europes-far-right/00000190-fe0f-d88d-adb8-ff3f1b910000</link><description>这个历史悠久的歌舞表演中的每一个图像都旨在描绘一个新的、多元文化的法国，对任何性别或性取向开放。组织者设法既杀死了神圣的牛又不留下干眼症</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 13:58:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-enrages-europes-far-right/00000190-fe0f-d88d-adb8-ff3f1b910000</guid></item><item><title>凯撒利亚之战：占领以色列最富裕社区之一的令人惊讶的冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-battle-of-caesarea-will-the-fall-of-netanyahus-rule-start-at-home/00000190-f9cd-da13-a5d5-fdff64930000</link><description>在总理居住的凯撒利亚，反内塔尼亚胡的抗议活动日益增多，在这座富裕的小镇引起了轩然大波。 “凯撒利亚反映了整个国家面临的问题——大量的仇恨和分裂，以及沉默的大多数”</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 12:56:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-battle-of-caesarea-will-the-fall-of-netanyahus-rule-start-at-home/00000190-f9cd-da13-a5d5-fdff64930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军拘留涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦囚犯的士兵后，极右翼MKs和抗议者袭击了斯德·泰曼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/idf-police-raid-sde-teiman-prison-detain-soldiers-suspected-of-abusing-detainee/00000190-fe2c-d22a-abfe-ff2c10c20000</link><description>据报道，以色列士兵与警察对峙并封锁自己，向前来拘留嫌疑人的军事人员喷洒胡椒粉，抗议者闯入拘留中心 ■ 消息人士称，这些士兵因有报道称他们虐待一名巴勒斯坦囚犯而被拘留</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 12:24:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/idf-police-raid-sde-teiman-prison-detain-soldiers-suspected-of-abusing-detainee/00000190-fe2c-d22a-abfe-ff2c10c20000</guid></item><item><title>在迈季代勒沙姆斯炸死 12 名儿童的火箭弹也触动了戈兰德鲁兹派与以色列之间关系的痛处</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/the-rocket-that-killed-12-children-hit-a-nerve-in-israels-relations-with-the-golan-druze/00000190-fe00-d22a-abfe-ff282afc0000</link><description>在经历了该社区历史上最悲惨的一天之后，戈兰高地德鲁兹人的独特处境凸显出来。夹在长期的叙利亚身份和与以色列日益加深的联系之间，尤其是在年轻人中，这个人口少而紧密的人口面临着不确定的未来</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 11:35:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/the-rocket-that-killed-12-children-hit-a-nerve-in-israels-relations-with-the-golan-druze/00000190-fe00-d22a-abfe-ff282afc0000</guid></item><item><title>美国警告黎巴嫩公民：“在危机开始之前离开”；航空公司取消飞往贝鲁特、特拉维夫的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/major-airlines-cancel-delay-flights-to-beirut-as-fear-of-major-israel-hezbollah-war-looms/00000190-fdb0-da13-a5d5-fdfb8c570000</link><description>汉莎航空、法航、土耳其航空、爱琴航空等主要航空公司决定推迟和取消飞往黎巴嫩唯一国际机场贝鲁特拉菲克·哈里里机场的航班</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 09:24:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/major-airlines-cancel-delay-flights-to-beirut-as-fear-of-major-israel-hezbollah-war-looms/00000190-fdb0-da13-a5d5-fdfb8c570000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队指挥官下令炸毁拉法水库。以色列国防军怀疑违反国际法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/idf-commanders-gave-order-to-blow-up-rafah-reservoir-army-suspects-breach-of-intl-law/00000190-fd90-d5ef-a5fe-ff9ec3ea0000</link><description>装甲兵炸毁水库的行为得到了指挥官的批准，但没有得到高级军官的同意。一名士兵在社交媒体上发布了视频，称其为“纪念安息日”。军方将决定是否展开正式调查</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 09:09:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/idf-commanders-gave-order-to-blow-up-rafah-reservoir-army-suspects-breach-of-intl-law/00000190-fd90-d5ef-a5fe-ff9ec3ea0000</guid></item><item><title>Majdal Shams 的杀戮场上：巨大而平静的悲伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-the-killing-field-in-majdal-shams-a-great-but-quiet-grief/00000190-fd05-d7a2-a9b0-ff656e950000</link><description>德鲁兹小镇迈季达勒沙姆斯 (Majdal Shams) 是一个风景如画、安静的山脚下的地方，在黎巴嫩发射的火箭弹袭击导致 12 名儿童和青少年死亡后，这座小镇陷入了彻底的震动。一位居民说：“他们是我们大家的孩子。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 08:47:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-the-killing-field-in-majdal-shams-a-great-but-quiet-grief/00000190-fd05-d7a2-a9b0-ff656e950000</guid></item><item><title>我出生在以色列。我哪儿也不去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/i-was-born-in-israel-i-am-not-going-anywhere/00000190-fd2e-da13-a5d5-fd7ff3750000</link><description>因为我也是土著，所以我不打算搬家。哈马斯不会让我行动，贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇或伊塔马尔·本-格维尔也不会</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 07:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/i-was-born-in-israel-i-am-not-going-anywhere/00000190-fd2e-da13-a5d5-fd7ff3750000</guid></item><item><title>11 岁德鲁兹男孩被确认为真主党火箭袭击的第 12 名受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/11-year-old-druze-boy-identified-as-12th-victim-of-hezbollah-rocket-attack/00000190-fb20-d43d-afd2-ff3a23a00000</link><description>对火箭袭击现场发现的证据进行的 DNA 测试证实了格瓦拉·易卜拉欣 (Gevara Ebraheem) 的死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 06:26:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/11-year-old-druze-boy-identified-as-12th-victim-of-hezbollah-rocket-attack/00000190-fb20-d43d-afd2-ff3a23a00000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯：内塔尼亚胡推迟停火协议，设定了拜登提案中的新条件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article-live/12th-victim-of-attack-identified-cabinet-authorizes-pm-to-determine-response/00000190-fc64-d7a2-a9b0-fe640b290006</link><description>黎巴嫩报道：无人机袭击摩托车造成三人受伤 ■ 以色列国防军参谋长哈莱维：闯入斯德泰曼是非法的，严重的；军警对士兵进行调查是其职责 ■ 法航效仿德国汉莎航空，取消往返贝鲁特的航班直至周二</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 03:15:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article-live/12th-victim-of-attack-identified-cabinet-authorizes-pm-to-determine-response/00000190-fc64-d7a2-a9b0-fe640b290006</guid></item><item><title>北方全面战争？以色列对 Majdal Shams 袭击的反应将是决定性因素</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/another-escalation-or-turning-point-weighing-next-steps/00000190-fafc-d87c-ab98-fffeefbf0000</link><description>以色列专家试图评估真主党可能采取的下一步行动，北部德鲁兹社区的灾难不会得不到解决。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 03:01:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/another-escalation-or-turning-point-weighing-next-steps/00000190-fafc-d87c-ab98-fffeefbf0000</guid></item><item><title>戈兰高地遭受袭击后，内塔尼亚胡推迟将生病和受伤的儿童从加沙疏散到阿联酋</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-delays-evacuation-of-sick-wounded-children-from-gaza-to-uae-after-golan-attack/00000190-fab3-d5ef-a5fe-fabf8c750000</link><description>以色列最初同意为数百名受伤儿童从加沙运送到阿联酋接受治疗提供便利。以色列人权医生协会称这一决定是“以色列政府对儿童生命的残酷游戏”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 19:25:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-delays-evacuation-of-sick-wounded-children-from-gaza-to-uae-after-golan-attack/00000190-fab3-d5ef-a5fe-fabf8c750000</guid></item><item><title>为了挽救人质谈判，以色列探索内塔尼亚胡要求阻止武装加沙人向北移动的选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/to-salvage-hostage-talks-israel-explores-options-to-block-armed-gazans-from-moving-north/00000190-fa94-dfcb-a1f3-fed5d6f60000</link><description>武装分子从加沙南部向北部的流动被视为内塔尼亚胡在人质协议中面临的主要挑战。随着摩萨德负责人从罗马与调解员的会谈中归来，以色列官员看到了哈马斯在谈判中灵活性增强的迹象</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 19:07:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/to-salvage-hostage-talks-israel-explores-options-to-block-armed-gazans-from-moving-north/00000190-fa94-dfcb-a1f3-fed5d6f60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对国会和以色列人质施展了残酷的老伎俩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-28/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahu-pulled-an-old-cruel-trick-on-congress-and-on-israels-hostages/00000190-fa3e-d43d-afd2-fe3ee7710000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡来到华盛顿，对释放人质的协议表现出乐观态度，然后——在以色列公众看到他在国会受到起立鼓掌后——决定恢复他的拒绝立场</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 18:29:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-28/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahu-pulled-an-old-cruel-trick-on-congress-and-on-israels-hostages/00000190-fa3e-d43d-afd2-fe3ee7710000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列准备打击真主党时，西方努力避免黎巴嫩爆发全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-prepares-to-strike-hezbollah-west-seeks-to-avert-all-out-war-in-lebanon/00000190-fa1e-d731-a9bf-ff7ec5e70000</link><description>外交消息人士告诉《国土报》，全面战争的威胁取决于真主党对以色列袭击黎巴嫩的反应。美国和法国正试图阻止以色列以贝鲁特或其他主要城市为目标，以报复迈季代勒沙姆斯袭击事件</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 17:32:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-prepares-to-strike-hezbollah-west-seeks-to-avert-all-out-war-in-lebanon/00000190-fa1e-d731-a9bf-ff7ec5e70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 296 天：外交官称正在努力阻止以色列袭击贝鲁特</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-296-diplomats-say-efforts-underway-to-avert-israeli-strike-on-beirut/00000190-fa5c-d10b-a3b8-ff7c53260000</link><description>数千人参加真主党在德鲁兹镇火箭弹袭击中丧生的 12 名儿童和青少年的葬礼 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡、国防部长加兰特表示真主党将付出沉重代价 ■ 伊朗警告以色列不要在黎巴嫩进行任何“新冒险” ■ 据报道真主党清理了前方的关键地点以色列的预期反应 ■ 这是战争进入 296 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 17:27:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-296-diplomats-say-efforts-underway-to-avert-israeli-strike-on-beirut/00000190-fa5c-d10b-a3b8-ff7c53260000</guid></item></channel></rss>